From: Lei Zhang <lei.zhang@amlogic.com>
Date: Fri, 7 Mar 2025 11:00:37 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] preempt_rt: correct vendor hook head file [1/1]

PD#SWPL-201692

Problem:
build break with preempt-rt enabled

Solution:
include necessry head file

Verify:
on A5

Change-Id: I6de9e6ac19cc02b74e30aecae480bf468e489438
Signed-off-by: Lei Zhang <lei.zhang@amlogic.com>
---
 kernel/locking/rwsem.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/kernel/locking/rwsem.c b/kernel/locking/rwsem.c
index d1ac321821aa..f301bd7813c0 100644
--- a/kernel/locking/rwsem.c
+++ b/kernel/locking/rwsem.c
@@ -28,6 +28,9 @@
 #include <linux/rwsem.h>
 #include <linux/atomic.h>
 #include <trace/events/lock.h>
+#ifdef CONFIG_AMLOGIC_PREEMPT_RT
+#include <trace/hooks/rwsem.h>
+#endif

 #ifndef CONFIG_PREEMPT_RT
 #include "lock_events.h"
